---
---

<section class="block block-tint" id="who-we-are">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="layout">
      <div class="left">
        <h2 class="reveal">About <span class="amber">the studio.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="right reveal d1">
        <p>
          <strong>Christopher Matthews</strong> started Swampy South Labs in New Orleans to do a particular kind of work: build software carefully, for people who'll actually depend on it.
        </p>
        <p>
          He brings eight years of building enterprise software and XR platforms to the work — including leading XR delivery at a Fortune 500 technology company, and shipping a patient-education app now in an active clinical study at a US hospital.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .container { max-width: var(--maxw); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--pad); }

  .block { padding: 140px 0; }
  .block-tint { background: var(--moss-50); }

  .layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .left h2 {
    font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 4.6vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 0; color: var(--bayou); max-width: 12ch;
  }
  .left h2 .amber { color: var(--amber-deep); }

  .right p {
    margin: 0 0 20px; color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 56ch;
  }
  .right p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .right strong { color: var(--bayou); font-weight: 600; }

  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  .reveal.d1 { transition-delay: .08s; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }
</style>
